# Hybrid SSR + SMT (Z3) OCL Verification — Full Extended

This package includes:
- SSR stubs (pre/post analyzers)
- Rich **OCL→SMT encoder** (bounded collections, enums, quantifiers)
- **Dynamic scope configuration** from `config/scopes.yaml`
- Orchestrator, reports, examples, tests

## Quick Start
```bash
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m ssr_ocl.cli verify --model examples/animal/model.xmi --ocl examples/animal/constraints.ocl
```
Artifacts are saved to `reports/runs/<timestamp>/`.
